sentences: Charlie Barnes (born 31 May 1989) is an English singer and songwriter.
He is a vocalist and multi-instrumentalist performing under his own name, and currently as a touring musician with indie rock band Bastille.
He has released three albums; the latest, Last Night's Glitter, was released in July 2020.
